description: Upload Custom Domain SSL certificate for an API Management service. This operation will be deprecated in future releases.

parameters.description: Parameters supplied to the Upload SSL certificate for an API Management service operation.

api_version.description: Version of the API to be used with the client request.

subscription_id.description: Subscription credentials which uniquely identify Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

expiry.description: Expiration date of the certificate. The date conforms to the following format: `yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ssZ` as specified by the ISO 8601 standard.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group.

service_name.description: The name of the API Management service.
